@startuml hypertrack_live-app-android

actor User
participant "Android App" as App
participant "CognitoClient" as Cognito
participant "BackendClientFactory" as Factory
participant "AbstractBackendProvider" as Backend
participant "HyperTrack SDK" as SDK
participant "AWS Cognito" as AWSCognito
participant "HyperTrack API" as HTAPI
participant "Google Maps" as Maps

User -> App : Open app
App -> Cognito : Initialize
Cognito -> AWSCognito : Authenticate user
AWSCognito --> Cognito : Authentication token
Cognito --> App : User authenticated

User -> App : Start location sharing
App -> Factory : Create backend client
Factory --> App : Backend client instance
App -> Backend : Create trip
Backend -> HTAPI : Create trip request
HTAPI --> Backend : Trip details
Backend --> App : Trip created

App -> SDK : Start tracking
SDK -> App : Location updates

loop Location Updates
    SDK -> App : New location
    App -> Maps : Update map
    App -> Backend : Update trip
    Backend -> HTAPI : Update trip
end

User -> App : Stop sharing
App -> SDK : Stop tracking
App -> Backend : Complete trip
Backend -> HTAPI : Complete trip request
HTAPI --> Backend : Trip summary
Backend --> App : Trip completed

App -> Maps : Display trip summary

@enduml